      <abstract encodinganalog="520$a" label="Abstract: ">
                    Papers of the American Methodist clergyman.  Consists of Fanton's sermons and their source material, usually 
					newspaper clippings, annotated with dates and places of delivery, all in New York State.</abstract>
      <unitid encodinganalog="099" label="Identification: " countrycode="US" repositorycode="NSyU">148970</unitid>
