    <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
      <head>Biographical History</head>
      <p>William N. Fanton was an American Methodist clergyman.</p>
    </bioghist>
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
      <head>Scope and Contents of the Collection</head>
      <p>The <emph render="bold">William N. Fanton Sermons</emph> consist of sermons and the material (usually newspaper clippings) 
	  which inspired Fanton to write these particular sermons.</p>
    </scopecontent>
    <arrangement encodinganalog="351$a">
      <head>Arrangement of the Collection</head>
      <p>Sermons are arranged chronologically.  Clippings are filed with the sermon which they inspired.</p>
    </arrangement>
